# 6. Feature Brief ဆိုတာဘာလဲ

Level 4 Agent ကို feature ခိုင်းမယ်ဆိုရင် prompt တစ်ကြောင်းနဲ့မလုံလောက်ပါဘူး။ **Feature Brief** လိုတယ်။

Feature Brief ဆိုတာ—

```text
Agent ကို feature တစ်ခုအတွက် ပေးတဲ့ mini SPEC
```

ပါ။

Feature Brief ထဲမှာ အနည်းဆုံးပါရမယ့်အပိုင်း—

```text
1. Feature name
2. Context
3. Goal
4. Scope
5. Non-goals
6. Acceptance criteria
7. Allowed files/folders
8. Do-not-touch list
9. Verification
10. Reporting format
```

ဥပမာ—

```md
# FEATURE_BRIEF.md

## Feature
Registration History

## Context
This is a static HTML/CSS/JS practice app for learning Level 4 Coding Agent workflow.

## Goal
When a user submits name and phone, the app should add an attendee record to a visible list and persist it in localStorage.

## Scope
- Frontend only
- No backend API
- No package install
- Use existing index.html, style.css, app.js

## Non-goals
- Email/SMS notification
- Database
- Authentication
- Deployment

## Acceptance Criteria
- Empty name shows Myanmar error
- Empty phone shows Myanmar error
- Valid submission generates ticket code
- Attendee appears in list
- Data remains after browser refresh
- Clear history button removes saved attendees
- Browser console has no errors

## Verification
- Manual browser tests
- git diff summary
```

Feature Brief ကောင်းရင် Coding Agent လမ်းမလွဲနိုင်ဘူး။

