# 11. Level 4 Prompt Anatomy

Level 4 Coding Agent prompt က Level 3 prompt ထက်ပိုပြည့်စုံရမယ်။

```text
1. Role
2. Mode
3. Feature brief
4. Scope
5. Non-goals
6. Allowed files/folders
7. Do-not-touch list
8. Workflow steps
9. Acceptance criteria
10. Verification
11. Reporting format
12. Approval gates
```

Example—

```text
Role:
သင်က careful coding agent ဖြစ်တယ်။

Mode:
Plan first. Code မပြင်သေးပါနဲ့။

Feature:
Registration History feature ထည့်ချင်ပါတယ်။

Context:
ဒီ app က static HTML/CSS/JS practice app ဖြစ်တယ်။

Goal:
Valid registration submit လုပ်ရင် attendee list ထဲထည့်ပြီး localStorage ထဲသိမ်းပါ။

Scope:
- Frontend only
- Existing files ပဲသုံးပါ
- Backend API မထည့်ပါ
- Package install မလုပ်ပါ

Allowed files:
- playground/chapter-11-coding-agent/index.html
- playground/chapter-11-coding-agent/style.css
- playground/chapter-11-coding-agent/app.js

Do not touch:
- package.json
- package-lock.json
- .env
